    <item>
      <title>Advent 考虑以 50 亿欧元出售仿制药制造商 Zentiva</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/advent-said-to-mull-5-billion-sale-of-generic-drugmaker-zentiva</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，收购公司 Advent International 正在考虑出售仿制药制造商 Zentiva，这笔交易对赛诺菲前子公司的估值可能达到约 50 亿欧元（54 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/advent-said-to-mull-5-billion-sale-of-generic-drugmaker-zentiva</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:08:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Polymarket 的法国鲸鱼赢得 4800 万美元特朗普大奖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/polymarket-s-french-whale-hits-48-million-us-election-jackpot-with-trump-s-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[许多参与加密货币市场的人士周三都有理由为唐纳德·特朗普的胜利而洋洋得意，但一位备受关注的法国交易员的赌注将为选举结果带来数百万美元的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/polymarket-s-french-whale-hits-48-million-us-election-jackpot-with-trump-s-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 17:50:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选后市场涨跌互现，油价难以找到方向</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价稳定在每桶 72 美元附近，与昨日相比变化不大，交易员对唐纳德·特朗普当选可能对市场产生的影响感到矛盾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 16:27:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选引发赤字担忧 市政债券价格暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/muni-bonds-tumble-after-trump-victory-ignites-deficit-worries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，在选民选举唐纳德·特朗普为美国总统后，市政债券价格暴跌。此前，美国国债价格暴跌，人们担心特朗普的政策将扩大本已膨胀的预算赤字并导致通胀飙升，导致美国国债遭到抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/muni-bonds-tumble-after-trump-victory-ignites-deficit-worries</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 15:07:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者如何应对特朗普的胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/wall-street-reacts-it-s-full-risk-on-as-trump-scores-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，随着唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 赢得美国总统第二任期，在与副总统卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 的势均力敌的角逐中，冒险狂潮席卷金融资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/wall-street-reacts-it-s-full-risk-on-as-trump-scores-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 14:12:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿斯利康称其现任和前任高管涉嫌中国调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/astra-says-current-former-executives-involved-in-china-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿斯利康公司表示，该集团中国公司的两名现任和两名前任高管因涉嫌违反药品进口和数据隐私相关法律而接受调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/astra-says-current-former-executives-involved-in-china-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 14:11:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选被视为美国企业利好，信贷市场反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/credit-markets-send-some-of-their-most-bullish-signals-in-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国总统大选后，全球信贷市场出现上涨，因为基金经理们准备减税和放松监管，以潜在地提高公司的盈利水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/credit-markets-send-some-of-their-most-bullish-signals-in-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:47:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
